  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "The bill codifies an individual's right to own, possess, and use a firearm to the maximum extent permissible by the state and federal constitutions.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Extreme risk protection orders and temporary extreme risk protection orders are repealed.(Note: This summary applies to this bill as introduced.)"
    }
  ],
